    "line": 3,
    "content": "This section provides a comprehensive analysis of the experimental results, examining the underlying mechanisms that drive A* algorithm performance across different scenarios and environmental conditions. We interpret the findings in the context of theoretical pathfinding principles and discuss their implications for practical applications."
