    "content": ""
  },
  {
    "line": 27,
    "content": "Scenario C demonstrates that A* maintains remarkable robustness across varying obstacle densities. The algorithm achieved a 100\\% success rate for obstacle densities up to 40\\%, with only a single failure at 50\\% density. The search time remained relatively stable (0.11-0.43 ms) across most density levels, increasing noticeably only at the extreme 50\\% density."
