    "content": "Within the 50×50 map scenarios, the differences are minimal, suggesting that heuristic choice, obstacle density, and path length have relatively modest effects on overall performance compared to map size. However, the heuristic comparison (Scenario B) shows that while search time differences are small, the node expansion differences are substantial (40.0 vs. 153.7 vs. 244.1 nodes). This indicates that heuristic choice primarily affects the search space exploration rather than the implementation overhead."
